    Section I: PREAMBLE

    The BigCode project seeks to develop and maintain large language models
    for code in an open and responsible manner. This license is designed to
    enable broad use of model weights derived from or trained on datasets
    governed by the BigCode OpenRAIL-M license (including StarCoderData),
    while establishing responsible use obligations.

    This license governs use of the BitDiffusion a4.8 model weights and
    any derivatives thereof. The model code (source files) is separately
    licensed under Apache 2.0. Only the trained model weights and
    derivatives of those weights are subject to this license.


